                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-stage">The Manifestation</span>
                    <h4 class="timeline-title">Enter Shyam</h4>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">A third wardrobe opens up to reveal a resident floating ghost complete with Ray-Bans and designer shoes, triggering an initial fainting spell[cite: 59, 64, 66].</p>
