            <div class="timeline-item">
                <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                <div class="timeline-content">
                    <span class="timeline-stage">The Climax</span>
                    <h4 class="timeline-title">The Ghostly Franchise Call</h4>
                    <p class="timeline-desc">Instead of running away, the survivors choose commercial optimization, transforming a historic curse into a highly profitable 300% booking machine[cite: 863, 866, 868, 892].</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ending-section">
        <span class="section-label">The Final Curtain</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading">Happily Ever After...ish</h2>
        <div class="ending-message">
            The ghosts may fade into shimmering gold mist or stay behind to prank the tourists, but one thing remains certain: true love is defined by who sticks around to hold your hand during an unexpected spiritual exorcism at 2 AM[cite: 236, 456, 873, 875, 876].
        </div>
        <div class="ending-quote">
            "Ciao... Adios... See you soon."
        </div>
        <p class="ending-reflection">
            The book closes on an expanding franchise empire, proving that when life hands you ancient architectural curses, the best response is always to package it with free Wi-Fi and put it directly on the market[cite: 20, 866, 892].
        </p>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <h3 class="footer-title">The Honeymoon Haunting</h3>
        <div class="footer-author">Deva Harsha V</div>
        <p class="footer-quote">"Where Love Meets the Unexpected... and Sometimes the Undead." [cite: 882]</p>
    </footer>

    <script>
        // Smooth scrolling active state on scroll
        const sections = document.querySelectorAll('section');
        const navItems = document.querySelectorAll('.nav-item');
        const navbar = document.getElementById('navbar');

        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            // Navbar contraction styling
            if (window.scrollY > 50) {
                navbar.classList.add('scrolled');
            } else {
                navbar.classList.remove('scrolled');
            }

            // Highlighting active section link
            let current = '';
            sections.forEach(section => {
                const sectionTop = section.offsetTop;
                const sectionHeight = section.clientHeight;
                if (window.scrollY >= (sectionTop - 150)) {
                    current = section.getAttribute('id');
                }
            });

            navItems.forEach(item => {
                item.classList.remove('active');
                if (item.getAttribute('href') === `#${current}`) {
                    item.classList.add('active');
                }
            });
        });
    </script>

